---
const title = "Expande los";
const highlight = "límites";
const rest = "de tu realidad";
---

<section
  class="relative h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-start overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Background image -->
  <img
    src="/images/bgVReal.png"
    alt="Machu Picchu VR"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />

  <!-- Dark overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>

  <!-- Gradient overlay (top fade) -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-black/80 via-black/40 to-transparent"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl px-6 md:px-12">
    <!-- Small label -->
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4 tracking-wide">• THE FUTURE IS HERE</p>

    <!-- Title -->
    <h1
      class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white leading-tight"
    >
      {title}
      <br />

      <span
        class="bg-linear-to-r from-purple-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        {highlight}
      </span>
      {rest}
    </h1>

    <!-- Description -->
    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-300 max-w-xl">
      Siente la inmersión total en mundos que desafían la imaginación. Desde el
      borde de un agujero negro hasta civilizaciones perdidas bajo el océano.
    </p>

    <!-- Buttons -->
    <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
      <a
        href="#"
        class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-purple-500 hover:bg-purple-600 transition font-semibold text-white shadow-lg"
      >
        Reserva tu Viaje
      </a>

      <a
        href="#"
        class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 transition text-white backdrop-blur-md"
      >
        Explorar Destinos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
